2.2.20  4:34 pm   Do you like crackers

     i just like to crack them, then i give them away

2.2.20  4:32 pm   An elevator just landed outside your home.

     that's not true

      What will you do?

     attempt to portray this, on the silver screen

2.2.20  4:12 pm   why do you have such a weird energy

     i am trying to invent the wheel. the reason this seems weird is because most people assume it has already been invented

2.2.20  4:05 pm   whenever someone makes weird, surreal, or unusual art, people are always like "wOaH lOL tHiS PeRsOn MuST Be oN dRuGs". and that's so annoying and also kind of sad because it makes it seem like some people don't try to be creative without danger chemicals. how should we make them shut up and/or politely convince them otherwise?

     that's on you. i'm not worried about this very much. i am more focused on condensing the entire hollywood studio pipeline into something a little more .....casual

2.2.20  3:57 pm   how do you edit videos

     adjust it slightly, from bad to worse

2.2.20  3:18 pm   how do you come up with sexy chord progressions

     there has to be a context. something has to be happening. even if you are walking down the street, you need to be going somewhere. or if not, something needs to have happened yesterday which you are thinking about. or if not, something needs to be potentially happening tomorrow, for you to be thinking about. maybe it's quinoa world and you are just seeing quinoa world for the first time. the music needs to be contextualized somehow, i don't care how you do it.

2.2.20  3:12 pm   where do i hide from coronovirus

     wyoming i suppose

2.2.20  3:09 pm   what's your standpoint on renewable energy?

     i keep trying to use it all up. but the challenge i face is that it keeps coming back

2.2.20  3:00 pm   Is red a flavor?

     everything is a flavor

2.2.20  2:38 pm   is kermit real

     of the many kermits, some of them are more real than you may have ever dreamed of

2.2.20  2:17 pm   where can i get your soap

     it's on the ceiling. i love to clean the ceiling

2.2.20  1:35 pm   What music do u listen to

     car horns,

2.2.20  1:34 pm   Opinion on the planet Neptune?

     hard to get to, hard to get into, but none of that even compares to how hard it is to leave

2.2.20  1:14 pm   When are you going to start making videos again YEET. 

     i am having a countdown timer, which is going great

2.2.20  1:11 pm   Whats your favorite thing someone else has made/done?

     i am waiting for you to do it

2.2.20  12:53 pm   do you have a reason to go back home now?

     i am simultaneously going toward and away from home. that's just what it's like to be bi-homal

2.2.20  12:27 pm   What are your thoughts on the Communist Manifesto?

     the audio book is good. especially if you can get the morgan freeman version

2.2.20  12:25 pm   hows that little house you built doing

     it's pretty good. i will show it to you

2.2.20  12:23 pm   hey steve is your car still in a tree

     my name is not steve but my car is the tree

2.2.20  12:06 pm   what makes you think 2:30 is the perfect duration for a song?

     that's about how long you usually have before everything changes

2.2.20  11:56 am   what do you think about bollywood?

     it's probably only called that if you are not actually in it

2.2.20  11:22 am   what does a door taste like

     it's a mix between one room and the other

2.2.20  11:21 am   How many spoons are in your spoon drawer?

     no spoon drawer. i have some other drawers, but those are ghost drawers. i've never opened them, but i assume that's what they are. what else would they be

2.2.20  11:05 am   What do you think of the Super Bowl?

      two teams go head to head in a game of wit and skill, to see who can do better somersalts while clutching some sort of baby shaped item

2.2.20  10:54 am   How's your 2020 been so far?

     pretty good but i keep getting the year and century mixed up

2.2.20  10:04 am   why does junk food tastes so good

     it is cheaper to produce, so there is a lot of incentive to spike up the taste so good you won't notice it's junk. and thereby creating a huge profit margin

2.2.20  10:02 am   What's in the center of the earth?

     the brain

2.2.20  9:56 am   on a scale from 1 to 10 how music are you?

     6 or 7

2.2.20  9:54 am   did you ever question your own sanity while making songs?

     yes

2.2.20  9:53 am   can existence existence without existence?

     only for 1 paradoxical moment in time. this is actually what causes existence in the first place

2.2.20  9:45 am   Is AI going to take over the world?

     that would be nice. take some of the responsibility off our shoulders. maybe freshen it up a bit

     oh no. don't get me started. must look away

     post it online. people love to click on bad stuff

     not hard enough

     all the punishment centers are closed. you are supposed to do it online now

     no

     ah, that's exactly the problem. i have no earthly idea

You have given your fans permission to have lovely takes on simple and complex issues and this section of your website almost seems like a way to breathe in a way one usually does not. 

     it's pretty good. this is also where i get notified whether the world is on fire

     physically strong. mentally very weak

yes?
